name: Titanium Backup File
summary: Learn about .TIBKP files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: To import a TIBKP file, press the menu button, select "import backup (TiBkp)," and choose the TIBKP file you want to import.
NOTE: Titanium Backup is available for free. Titanium Backup PRO, which must be purchased, unlocks additional features.

description: Backup file created by Titanium Backup, an application used to back up files on Android devices; contains a backup of an app with related data or just the data itself; stored locally and can be exported to other devices.
